cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SE 

This paper deals with termination analysis of numerical computations in logic programs, which is a topic closely related to programming languages (cs.PL) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also discusses the integration of techniques for analysis of numerical computations with the framework of acceptability, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of constraint-based approach to termination also relates to data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
